name: Ext_R3_ImplementationGuide_pa_re_example
title: Cross-version Extension for R3.ImplementationGuide.package.resource.example for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version extension represents ImplementationGuide.package.resource.example from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/ImplementationGuide|3.0.2 for use in FHIR R5.

element.short: If not an example, has its normal meaning
element.definition: Whether a resource is included in the guide as part of the rules defined by the guide, or just as an example of a resource that conforms to the rules and/or help implementers understand the intent of the guide.
element.comment: `ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.example[x]` maps to R5 `ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.isExample`. To multiple elements in ImplementationGuide: (`ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.isExample`, `ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.profile`). Type `canonical(http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/StructureDefinition)` has no mapping So is mapped as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget. `ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.example[x]` maps to R5 `ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.profile`. To multiple elements in ImplementationGuide: (`ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.isExample`, `ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.profile`). Type `boolean` has no mapping Changed from a single value to an array (max cardinality from 1 to *). So is mapped as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget.
